Download agent from:
https://packages.wazuh.com/4.x/windows/wazuh-agent.msi
Install it.

During installation enter:
Manager IP : 192.168.1.10

After installation open PowerShell as Administrator....

Import the key:
"C:\Program Files (x86)\ossec-agent\agent-auth.exe" -m 192.168.1.10

Start service:
net start wazuh

Check connection:
services.msc
